('Understanding Heart Disease: Prevention and Management', 'Learn about the latest advances in heart disease prevention, diagnosis, and treatment options.', 'Heart disease remains the leading cause of death worldwide. This comprehensive guide covers everything from risk factors to cutting-edge treatments including lifestyle modifications, medication management, and surgical interventions.', 'Cardiology', 'Dr. Emily Carter', 'https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/1.jpg', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=800&h=400&fit=crop', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=400&h=250&fit=crop', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL 1 DAY, '8 min read', 2345, 189, 45, true, true, 'understanding-heart-disease', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
('5 Signs You Should See a Cardiologist', 'Do not ignore these warning signs that could indicate serious heart problems.', 'Early detection of heart conditions can save lives. Here are 5 critical signs that require immediate attention from a cardiologist: chest pain, shortness of breath, palpitations, dizziness, and swelling in the legs.', 'Cardiology', 'Dr. Emily Carter', 'https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/1.jpg', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=800&h=400&fit=crop', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=400&h=250&fit=crop', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL 3 DAY, '6 min read', 1876, 156, 34, false, true, 'signs-see-cardiologist', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
('Heart Surgery: What to Expect', 'A comprehensive guide to preparing for and recovering from heart surgery.', 'Heart surgery can be daunting. This guide walks you through every step of the journey from pre-operative preparation to post-surgical recovery and long-term care.', 'Cardiology', 'Dr. James Wilson', 'https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/2.jpg', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=800&h=400&fit=crop', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=400&h=250&fit=crop', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL 2 DAY, '10 min read', 1567, 134, 28, true, true, 'heart-surgery-guide', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
